{"tid":1249859,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[算吧啦六師弟]【EA：我們不會放棄《冒險聖歌》 Bioware需要進步】","createTime":"2019-06-22T00:06:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-22T22:01:56.000Z","uid":75050,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a679c80ae738b9a490e2cdb7698a01a6f7e23214","tid":1249859,"uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T00:06:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/Nmia.Gaming/posts/1269606016540607\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FNmia.Gaming%2Fposts%2F1269606016540607&d=ow9JOMNIA3MeF92spim0Ptgc6rz%2Ba6PLwHdujBQ9FQE%3D&h=f9036ce5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/Nmia.Gaming/posts/1269606016540607</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wJH4pYr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwJH4pYr.jpg&h=35df4718&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nEA的CEO Andrew Wilson近日在接受GameDaily采訪時表示：「IP的生命周期至少有7-10年。所以如果你把《冒險聖歌》放在十年周期裡看，盡管它的開局不盡人意，但是我認為開發團隊最終還是能打造出一款特殊而偉大的作品。」<br />\n<br />\nWilson提到這款遊戲很大一個問題在於玩家群體的割裂，有人偏向於類似《質量效應》的敘事體驗，有人則想更進一步的動作冒險玩法，這對公司而言是始料未及的。<br />\n<br />\n說道Bioware，Wilson則認為他們需要不斷取得進步，從而滿足不同年代玩家的需求：「Bioware開發許多不同的遊戲，甚至有很多12歲開始就一直追隨的核心粉絲。但是這些孩子已經長大了，對於Bioware也有了更多的期待。因此他們也需要不斷地進化、拓展並且測試自身品牌的彈性。遊戲的開發團隊每天都會繼續他們的工作，傾聽不同年齡段玩家的意見。這就《冒險聖歌》在今天所要做的事情。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cjmXKYt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcjmXKYt.jpg&h=759f67c5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a317e6076e12f402c5764e8b67a0435a562fd902","tid":1249859,"uid":23468,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T04:15:33.000Z","msg":"糞EA食多D屎啦，唔係我地放棄隻GAME,係我地放棄EA"},{"pid":"ee2fc49c9b0491673ce50adfffde19e8fddba28f","tid":1249859,"uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T11:27:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b0dc708dfefefad086989ab01aa606b9dbee6a6","tid":1249859,"uid":285,"like":0,"